<br>
Also, we have killed him many times and know exactly how to move him arround, so if it is your frist time, I'd take a good 40 50 people if you can.  My bigest suggestion is, if you mess up, unless you have an immediate recovery,  zone it.  The time you save from rebuffing is more than worth it.<br>
<br>
Also don't try to recover if your clerics get AEed.  It almost becomes pointless.<br>
